{"no":104,"name":"سُورَةُ الهُمَزَةِ","enName":"Al-Humaza","enNameTranslation":"The Traducer","bnNameTranslation":"আল হুমাযা","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":9,"verses":[{"text":"وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍ","bnText":"প্রত্যেক পশ্চাতে ও সম্মুখে পরনিন্দাকারীর দুর্ভোগ","enText":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","enTextTransliteration":"Wai lul-li kulli hu mazatil-lumaza","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6180","numberInSurah":1},{"text":"الَّذِي جَمَعَ مَالًا وَعَدَّدَهُ","bnText":"যে অর্থ সঞ্চিত করে ও গণনা করে","enText":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it.","enTextTransliteration":"Al-lazi jama'a maalaw wa'addadah","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6181","numberInSurah":2},{"text":"يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُ أَخْلَدَهُ","bnText":"সে মনে করে যে, তার অর্থ চিরকাল তার সাথে থাকবে","enText":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal.","enTextTransliteration":"Yahsabu anna maalahu akhladah","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6182","numberInSurah":3},{"text":"كَلَّا ۖ لَيُنبَذَنَّ فِي الْحُطَمَةِ","bnText":"কখনও না, সে অবশ্যই নিক্ষিপ্ত হবে পিষ্টকারীর মধ্যে।","enText":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher.","enTextTransliteration":"Kalla layum ba zanna fil hutamah","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6183","numberInSurah":4},{"text":"وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْحُطَمَةُ","bnText":"আপনি কি জানেন, পিষ্টকারী কি","enText":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher?","enTextTransliteration":"Wa maa adraaka mal-hutamah","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6184","numberInSurah":5},{"text":"نَارُ اللَّهِ الْمُوقَدَةُ","bnText":"এটা আল্লাহর প্রজ্জ্বলিত অগ্নি","enText":"It is the fire of Allah, [eternally] fueled,","enTextTransliteration":"Narul laahil-mooqada","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6185","numberInSurah":6},{"text":"الَّتِي